Character Palette is a Firefox extension for inputing special characters,
licensed under GNU GPLv3.

Character Palette uses git as its version control system, hosted at github:
http://github.com/ryanli/charpick

For official stable versions, you could download at the following AMO link:
http://github.com/ryanli/charpick/downloads

You can get the latest development files using the following command:
$ git clone git://github.com/ryanli/charpick.git

If you have any problem using this software, you can create an issue in
the github homepage.

---
Ryan Li <ryan@ryanium.com>
